{"tid":299802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[習總訪港]維園英殖遺物封上圍板 避免習來港時看到","createTime":"2017-06-27T11:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T01:28:47.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6938474aa1b1382155d4287faa54b38978719fd","tid":299802,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平將於周四訪港3日，警方近日已在灣仔佈防，設置大型水馬等保安措施，灣仔區議員楊雪盈今日在facebook上載一張相片，指維園內的維多利亞女王銅像外圍被封上圍板，令人質疑是為習近平到訪做準備，避免習來港時看到英殖遺物。<br />\n<br />\n有網民對圍板行動表示憤怒，有人反問中央是否「一個舊銅像也容不下？氣量少得可憐了！」，有人揶揄建議維多利亞公園亦要改名，避開英殖文化，有人甚至笑言可能名稱擁英殖特色的街道亦不可行經。<br />\n在銅鑼灣維園的維多利亞女王銅像已有逾120年歷史，銅像去年因油漆剝落，政府曾委託承辦商復修，但復修物料太厚令銅像細節消失，銅像顏色變深，惹來批評做法不專業。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170627/56883692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170627%2F56883692&d=IyI1X4%2B9V8iOwi6JoPChzUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0d2b5548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170627%2F56883692&h=1c7b9778\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170627/56883692</a>"},{"pid":"f19d4c0a698949ae9c9f7ce612a77573592ceb74","tid":299802,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"玻璃心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40282bc12fdb97529a34e4cf968d7cb8f09559f","tid":299802,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"佢唔直接拆咗佢好好㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc33fefedc43d434e3d92aa4b91eea31b93705c","tid":299802,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"好明顯係下面班人諗出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\